sequenceDiagram
    participant MLApp as ML Application
    participant OnlineSvc as Online Store Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP or 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OnlineDB as Online Store Backend<br/>(SQLite/Redis/PostgreSQL)
    participant Pipeline as ML Training Pipeline
    participant OfflineSvc as Offline Store Service<br/>80/TCP HTTP or 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OfflineDB as Offline Store Backend<br/>(Dask/DuckDB/PostgreSQL/Snowflake)
    participant Client as Feast Client/CLI
    participant RegistrySvc as Registry Service<br/>80/TCP gRPC or 443/TCP gRPC+TLS
    participant RegistryDB as Registry Backend<br/>(File/SQLite/PostgreSQL/Snowflake)
    participant Operator as Feast Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over MLApp,OnlineDB: Flow 1: Online Feature Retrieval
    MLApp->>OnlineSvc: POST /get-online-features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: K8s RBAC / OIDC / None
    OnlineSvc->>OnlineDB: Query features<br/>Protocol: Various<br/>Auth: Secret-based credentials
    OnlineDB-->>OnlineSvc: Feature values
    OnlineSvc-->>MLApp: Feature response (JSON)

    Note over Pipeline,OfflineDB: Flow 2: Offline Feature Retrieval (Training)
    Pipeline->>OfflineSvc: Arrow Flight RPC request<br/>HTTP/TLS<br/>Auth: K8s RBAC / OIDC / None
    OfflineSvc->>OfflineDB: Historical feature query<br/>Protocol: Various<br/>Auth: Secret-based credentials
    OfflineDB-->>OfflineSvc: Historical feature data
    OfflineSvc-->>Pipeline: Arrow Flight response (columnar data)

    Note over Client,RegistryDB: Flow 3: Registry Metadata Management
    Client->>RegistrySvc: gRPC Registry RPC<br/>gRPC/TLS<br/>Auth: K8s RBAC / OIDC / None
    RegistrySvc->>RegistryDB: CRUD operations<br/>Protocol: Various<br/>Auth: Secret-based credentials
    RegistryDB-->>RegistrySvc: Metadata result
    RegistrySvc-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 4: FeatureStore CR Reconciliation
    K8sAPI->>Operator: FeatureStore CR event<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resources<br/>(Deployments, Services, ConfigMaps,<br/>PVCs, RBAC, Routes)<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Reconciliation complete
